name: Peptide Sequencer using Mass Specrometer
short_description:
This Project helps to predict the sequence of protein using the Mass Spectrometric result.
It also try to predict the sequence of peptide even if it is protected from other protecting groups like BOC, FMOC , Z, Acetyl, etc.
